  m_text: "How To Play:\n\n- Click 'n' Drag anywhere on the screen to launch the
    axolotl to the next platform.\n\n- The further you pull back, the more water
    taken away from your waterbar.\n\n- Pick Up Water Droplets to refill your waterbar.\n\n-
    Reach the pond at the end to pass!\n Good Luck & Stay Moist!\n\n"
